<sentence id="8">Genes involved in liver processes such as xenobiotic metabolism ( CYP3A4 , CYP3A5 , and CYP3A7 ) and steroid biosynthesis ( CYP17A1 and CYP19A1 ) , and genes encoding CCAAT element-binding proteins ( C/EBPalpha , C/EBPbeta , and C/EBPgamma ) were affected by 5-aza-dC or the combination .</sentence>
